comments: Davis (LAL) and Valanciunas (MEM) make incidental contact with each other going for the loose ball.
Valancuinas (MEM) is in the paint for less than three seconds prior to exiting.
James (LAL) makes contact with the ball during Clarke's (MEM) shot attempt near the rim.
Melton (MEM) makes contact to Davis' (LAL) arm and the contact affects his driving shot attempt.
Kuzma (LAL) maintains a legal guarding position during Brooks' (MEM) jump shot attempt.
Bane (MEM) commits a take foul on James (LAL).
Kuzma (LAL) makes contact to Jones' (MEM) arm and the contact affects his driving shot attempt.
Clarke (MEM) makes incidental hand on ball contact with James (LAL) as he dislodges the ball.
Melton (MEM) jumps backwards into Matthews (LAL) to go for the steal and the contact is incidental.  Matthews does not dislodge Melton from his position.
